Esquadrão Classe A — Plugin marketplace for Claude Code
=======================================================

This project packages and adapts, in the Claude Code plugin-marketplace format,
specialist agent "squads". Source content comes from two open-source projects:

    ohmyjahh/xquads-squads  —  https://github.com/ohmyjahh/xquads-squads
    Original author: Synkra AIOS  (12 squads)

    TheDecipherist/claude-code-mastery  —  https://github.com/TheDecipherist/claude-code-mastery
    Original author: TheDecipherist, MIT  (reference material for the
    `claude-code-mastery` squad: templates, hooks, commands, skills, guide)

