CLAUDE-CODE-MASTERY SQUAD
-------------------------
The `claude-code-mastery` squad bundles MIT-licensed reference material
(templates, hooks, slash commands, skills, and the guide) from
TheDecipherist/claude-code-mastery (Copyright (c) 2025 TheDecipherist). The MIT
license text is preserved in
`claude-code-mastery/skills/claude-code-mastery/LICENSE-thedecipherist`. The
squad's specialist personas, tasks, and orchestration (SKILL.md) are original
work by Anderson de Oliveira Venturini. All 13 squads in this marketplace are
MIT-licensed.

ADAPTATION
----------
The orchestration layer (`SKILL.md` files), commands, marketplace identity, and
differentiation of the orchestrator agents are adaptation work by
Anderson de Oliveira Venturini. Specialist personas based on public/historical
figures (copywriters, investors, etc.) remain references to those real figures.

USE
---
Personal/private marketplace. See README.md for installation instructions and
the list of squads.
